Rarity List

This is the 2024 rarity list for all of the countryballs. You can find the rarity for most balls here. If you want to use the old lists for any reason, view the Alternate Rarity Lists page.

Information

- This list was made by the Ballsdex wiki community. It is one of the most accurate and updated lists.

- As of April 21, 2024, the rarity list has been updated to include the new wave.
